videos.description: Zia Cooke drives hard to the basket and manages to split the NC State defenders to bank a shot high off the backboard and in for South Carolina.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Zia Cooke splits defenders for Gamecocks layup) 2020/12/03 ESHEET

videos.headline: Zia Cooke splits defenders for Gamecocks layup

videos.description: South Carolina's Laeticia Amihere comes up big, shutting down Kayla Jones' layup attempt by powerfully tossing it out of bounds.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Laeticia Amihere swats NC State layup attempt out of bounds) 2020/12/03 ESHEET

videos.headline: Laeticia Amihere swats NC State layup attempt out of bounds

videos.description: NC State's Kayla Jones comes up clutch draining a 3-pointer from deep to extend the Wolfpack lead to 51-46 over South Carolina with 27 seconds remaining.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Kayla Jones sinks dagger 3 as NC State snaps South Carolina's 29-game win streak) 2020/12/03 ESHEET
